?<br />\n當1:1... (百家樂算係最接近1:1)<br />\n以100蚊舖為例, 連開15舖都買輸, 要準備1,638,400賭本 (我當賭場冇上限)<br />\n而根據條賭方, 必嬴(超高概率)係幾錢? $100...<br />\n而只要第16舖都輸... 就......."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:36:39.000Z","msg":"我覺得仲有一個原因係風險管理，屌你無啦啦有條友抬幾百萬一注同你賭身家，其他賭仔都係幾百一千一注，對莊家條數同心理上既風險構成壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"308832a6bef29707bccb3f05e0881283c08a15b5","tid":2442322,"uid":110846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf1617d25d1fc3eb7412840e06610be53c3a7b02","tid":2442322,"uid":238973,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"8968d22781a51787d0b699e831784bb566b880a5","tid":2442322,"uid":159448,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:35:03.000Z","msg":"連開7鋪之後先買對家 穩陣啲"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:37:23.000Z","msg":"3次以上已經好大機會 唔使等7次<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:39:07.000Z","msg":"未去過澳門？ 成日連開10幾口<br />\n最高23口都 見過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7721a17024df4f25ac485d6c29a61b9446485e68","tid":2442322,"uid":215069,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"357b56db46ffdff990b93c899fa040616d93a586","tid":2442322,"uid":238973,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"a4502e17688bb40f59537174cafbd562591d70ac","tid":2442322,"uid":132758,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"277d5c34dcce689470d64d229264201dfe541590","tid":2442322,"uid":238973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:32:15.000Z","msg":"玩百家樂見到莊/閒連開三次之後就瘋狂買對家 輸一次就翻倍金額落注 例如第一次1蚊輸就買2蚊再輸就買4蚊 直到開到對家為止<br />\n最後點都贏到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 是否發達大計<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:36:37.000Z","msg":"如果你有無限資金可以.<br />\n如果唔係就只會輸光。"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:38:43.000Z","msg":"點會 連開5次以上既機率已經係超低<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"