stem%29?wprov=sfla1</a><br />\n<br />\n有詳細解釋你個方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc7d2391d4114247e3c23f706cdaa2d4cdbddb90","tid":2442322,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:26:42.000Z","msg":"見過連開17鋪閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ac2e264a9ea34e7245ef26686477c16bd30cd1","tid":2442322,"uid":131323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58319b4a21bcf29a409195d96004892095939f76","tid":2442322,"uid":186074,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:00:16.000Z","msg":"好多傻閪連澳門都未去過係度鳩up<br />\n<br />\n個個場大堂限紅標準都唔同    500蚊起手  <br />\n複式計  連輸13口已經限紅   渣都冇<br />\n想繼續追  上貴賓廳    再輸6.7口跳樓都唔掂<br />\n<br />\n呢d方法只適合玩機  次次贏廿蚊就要平注<br />\n如果冇限紅  李嘉誠一早納曬成個澳門黎玩啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:32:35.000Z","msg":"賭場除左驚你一口打爆個莊之外<br />\n100萬第一注 連輸5口第6口已經要3200萬<br />\n比你嬴番都係嬴100萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e9de5b02b9663f5fbef9338c7b30dbc3f696b84","tid":2442322,"uid":141869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"662bd643efb0191acafbc1e6e3e08d71c3145981","tid":2442322,"uid":48500,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:34:55.000Z","msg":"注碼過左上限點算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:32:48.000Z","msg":"重新來過咪得，唔會次次都爆上限，<br />\n想發達唔慳得"},{"pid":"24cff91dd1e4c52396928298782d38e30dabce98","tid":2442322,"uid":387132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:36:36.000Z","msg":"千日斬柴，一日燒"},{"pid":"78cd926b433d229e152dcf766a6ed4a0f7636f82","tid":2442322,"uid":300782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:39:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb7c6a455890e9c5b6247d614d4c059198cbcdf","tid":2442322,"uid":308853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:40:26.000Z","msg":"賭場會斬你手指"},{"pid":"10159116f39368b